ActNational Round Table on the Environment and the Economy Act
PrecisAppointment of DAVID VICTOR JOHN BELL of Thornhill, Ontario, ALFRED PILON of Deux-Montagnes, Quebec, and WENDY L. CARTER of North Vancouver, British Columbia, to be members of the National Round Table on the Environment and the Economy, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years.
